command to follow:   

 docker pull mysql
   docker run --name Rohit -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=Rohit123  -d mysql:tag .....to launch mysql container with password  Rohit123  .... -e for enviroment setting
    docker images
    docker ps -a
    docker pull wordpress
    
    docker run --name rohitkumar --link Rohit:mysql -p 8085:80 wordpress  ....it will link the wordpress container with mysql(as a database)
   docker ps -a


